Expectations of Epic

1. I expect to meet many new people.
    - I expect to make friends with many of these people.

2. I expect to learn about industry security standards.
    - Coming from the academic side, I want to see what happens outside of security research.

3. I expect to join "clubs" soon.

4. I expect to have free time to explore the campus.

5. I expect to have time to work on side projects and not be burned out from all the required work I have to do.

6. I expect to quickly pass through the introductory phase of the company. 

7. I expect to work efficiently on my assigned tasks.

8. I expect to keep my work at work, and have a separate personal life.

9. I expect to be respected for my opinions on my team.

10. ...
